<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Harry Potter - Weasley's Wares</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
For God knows what reason, the Harry Potter video games use Bertie Bott's Every Flavor Beans as money at Hogwarts instead of the standard wizarding currency Knuts, Sickles, and Galleons.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="t8vvh1">
<input type="hidden" name="is_logged_in" value="0">
<p>How well does it match the trope?</p>
